The ancestry was 9.4% [[English Americans|English]], 8.2% [[German Americans|German]], 7.7% [[Irish Americans|Irish]], 1.5% [[Scottish Americans|Scottish]], 1.3% [[Polish Americans|Polish]], and 0.7% [[Norwegian Americans|Norwegian]].<ref name=":0" />

The median age was 42.8 years old. 19.2% of the population were older than 65, with 10.1% between the ages of 65 and 74, and 9.1% between the ages of 75 and 84.<ref name=":0" />

The median household income was $46,125, with non-families having $36,761. 2.1% of the population were in poverty.<ref name=":0" />

